<meta name="flags" content="ahem"/>
<style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
body>div {
	font-family: ahem;
	font-size: 1em;
	line-height: 1em;
	color: white;
	width: 14em;
	height: 8em;

	column-count: 2;
	column-gap: 2em;
	column-fill: auto;
	column-rule: 10px solid blue;
}
]]></style>
</head>

<body>
<p>Below you should see TWO vertically-aligned, thin blue blocks of
equal height</p>

<div>
aaa aaa aaa aaa aaa aaa
